    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>Owns the single recv() loop and fans out messages to queues.

- Control-plane messages (msgpack dict with a &apos;type&apos;) go to control/error queues.
- Binary state buffers are pushed to state_queue, keeping only the latest.
</verbatim> </para>
